@baseUrl = http://localhost:8081
@token = {{login.response.body.data.accessToken}}

### 로그인 — 성공
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@graphify.dev",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### GET /history/{sessionId} — 성공 (목록에서 sessionId 교체)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/history/me?page=0&size=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### GET /history/{sessionId} — 성공 (첫 번째 세션)
@sessionId = REPLACE_WITH_SESSION_ID_FROM_LIST
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/history/{{sessionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### GET /history/{sessionId} — 실패 (없는 세션)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/history/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### GET /history/{sessionId} — 실패 (미인증)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/history/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

###
